quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,The Sudden Calamity
  101,2,What is the Sudden Calamity
  101,3,And what do you know what the Sudden Calamity is
  101,4,It is a Day when mankind shall be like the scattered moths
  101,5,And the mountains like fluffed up wool
  101,6,"That person, then, who weighs heavy [with good deeds] on the scales"
  101,7,"[That person] shall have a pleasant life"
  101,8,"And that person, who weighs light [because of bad deeds] on the scales"
  101,9,The Abyss then shall be his home
  101,10,"And what do you understand what it [the Abyss] is"
  101,11,A Fire intensely hot